| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1576 — Recovery Inhibition (blacknevas)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 70ca9a7a-57f4-5dff-865f-fa63a5a292c2"
